Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.risk.model.Player

  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    This Player Model represents a Player during our GamePlay. In terms of Strategy design Pattern this is our Context Class having an attribute for Strategy *
    Version:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Himansi Patel, Mayank Jariwala - Added Model Description
